== Overview ==

Android app + Image Recognition of Magic the Gathering playing cards for purposes of inventory and pricing.

== Installing ==

After pulling down this project, ensure you pull down the submodules.
<pre>git submodule update --init</pre>

<p>Import <i>android_mtg_card_scan</i> into eclipse.</p>
<p>Import <i>android_mtg_card_scan/android_libopencv</i> into eclipse.</p>

